        <h3>Q. Will I learn JavaScript at Devschool?</h3>

        <p>A. JavaScript is a scripting language built into every browser on the market today.
        Any "rich application" features that are interactive without a page-load, yep that was
        our friend JavaScript. We teach jQuery, along with 'vanilla' JavaScript and also
        ReactJS.</p>

        <p>JavaScript is said to be the "Next Big Thing" by many, many smart developers
